org.deeplearning4j.zoo.model.helper

Class FaceNetHelper

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.zoo.model.helper.FaceNetHelper

  • public class FaceNetHelper
extends java.lang.Object
    Inception is based on GoogleLeNet configuration of convolutional layers for optimization of resources and learning. You can use this module to add Inception to your own custom models. The GoogleLeNet paper: https://arxiv.org/abs/1409.4842 This module is based on the Inception GraphBuilderModule built for Torch and a Scala implementation of GoogleLeNet. https://github.com/Element-Research/dpnn/blob/master/Inception.lua https://gist.github.com/antikantian/f77e91f924614348ea8f64731437930d
